window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Now a complete audiobook series!</p> <p>When a detective with a penchant for chaos gets saddled with a new partner, a case that doesn’t make sense, and some particularly determined assassins…justice feels out of reach.</p> <p>Logan Blackwell has been a detective for a long time. After all, mages live for centuries. He lost his parents to the Mage Wars and his best friend to organized crime.</p> <p>When a powerful member of the vampire mafia robs a bank and a werewolf breaks into a jewelry store, Logan finds himself teaming up with a mysterious new partner, with a strong belief in rules, to uncover the truth behind these bizarre crimes.</p> <p>But as they delve deeper into the case, they soon realize that the corruption runs far deeper than they ever imagined. With unexpected twists and turns, this audiobook will keep you on the edge of your seat until the very end.</p> <p>If you enjoy urban fantasy novels that feature snarky male protagonists, strong female characters, and an anime vibe, then you’ll love this fast-paced series.</p> <p>Grab your copy and start bingeing the first three books in this complete five-book series today!</p>"; 
